The Alex Salmond Show is a Scottish weekly political talk show hosted by former First Minister of Scotland, Alex Salmond which premiered on RT on November 16, 2017. The guests includes various of political and public figures.
The show airs every Thursday on RT UK at 07:30, 12:30 and 22:30. The show is produced by Slainte Media, a production company co-owned by Salmond and former SNP MP Tasmina Ahmed-Sheikh.


